{"tid":2176582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青協指有青少年誤解大麻傷害 籲加強教育糾正失實資訊","createTime":"2020-08-27T07:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T00:13:11.000Z","uid":166360,"like":5,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9be74822d13f72280c85f7e595c75120e8d83b88","tid":2176582,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"青協指有青少年誤解大麻傷害 籲加強教育糾正失實資訊<br />\n2020-08-27 HKT 12:56<br />\n<br />\n&quot;一項有關青少年對大麻的認知及態度的調查發現，部分青少年對大麻存在明顯誤解，近3成半受訪者認為大麻對大腦的傷害比煙酒少，逾3成表示因為部分國家將消遣用大麻合法化，所以大麻帶來的傷害不大，亦有近3成不同意大麻是毒品......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;青協深宵青年服務單位主任李智廣......指出，大麻的禍害不容忽視，長期和大量使用會損害大腦發展及降低智力，吸食大麻亦有機會造成情緒大起大落&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546178-20200827.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546178-20200827.htm&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=3d44cd07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546178-20200827.htm&h=6d2f9b16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546178-20200827.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2f85f0de95bf61866d12e9d10324b15faf2ce41a","tid":2176582,"uid":79793,"like":36,"dislike":8,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"得啦 又想污名化大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0337339712a30a98cbf04bfb8c6e528303757c","tid":2176582,"uid":220942,"like":29,"dislike":7,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"咁點解外國可以大麻合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c04720d8190264317868af1e1f201d1007ebc3","tid":2176582,"uid":156542,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"青協戇鳩鳩 <br />\n唔識咪撚扮識啦"},{"pid":"028d8366aef6c8