dBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:15:23.000Z","msg":"你朋友到底食咗咩？<br />\n食大麻個人會好stone坐咗喺到<br />\n長期食就長期stone, 同你描述嘅朋友好相反"},{"pid":"4f0c4e4297b8e42675021db0b70a67820600b201","tid":2176582,"uid":208376,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:24:19.000Z","msg":"on9飲水飲得多都會中水毒，正常使用根本無問題"},{"pid":"37bc44c377aecc8356b125c70f85869d3ea37c91","tid":2176582,"uid":78519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b890f3e1ef84247dae1a7239133a8d433fb8409","tid":2176582,"uid":203889,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"bc0337339712a30a98cbf04bfb8c6e528303757c","tid":2176582,"uid":220942,"like":29,"dislike":7,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"咁點解外國可以大麻合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T19:04:36.000Z","msg":"其實青協無講錯<br />\n如果份量唔岩，或者長期食，係會影響身體<br />\n<br />\n不過唔止大麻，其他substance都會有負面影響但合法，例如煙酒<br />\n淨係禁大麻唔禁煙，雙重標準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:34:11.000Z","msg":"所以全部禁晒佢<br />\n等你班毒友咪喺度嘈生晒"},{"pid":"feebe7048829678b9f95d06642bd97ddd0020919","tid":2176582,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:36:09.000Z","msg":"邊個支持大麻合法化就係等於左膠"},{"pid":"c7296101d4055387369d55a84fdea0c2a1222922","tid":2176582,"uid":237005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:42:49.000Z","msg":"陳X柱mode: 點解你唔問青少年對香煙同酒精有誤解？係咪因為佢地合法就無傷害？<br />\n<br />\n既然大麻有害要禁，煙同酒都應該要禁"},{"pid":"fe73410bce5fe8eeb97e55757cc41bf7208eabf1","tid":2176582,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:43:11.000Z","msg":"經常使用大麻的人約有10%會發生大麻成癮。亦有相關醫學人士稱針對大麻成癮並無有效藥物可治療，多數是通過使用者自身的意志力。<br />\n<br />\n濫用大麻會導致眼紅、焦慮、妄想等諸多生理、心理的症狀，而出現大麻成癮的多數情況與使用者自身的心理健康問題有關，如對於心理亞健康人士或精神疾病患者來說，停止使用大麻比較困難。<br />\n<br />\n有研究表明大腦仍在發育的時候吸食大麻可能對神經發育和後來的認知功能產生有害影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E6%88%90%E7%98%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2598%25BE&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=5059e902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E6%88%90%E7%98%BE</a>"},{"pid":"c4c8f8c211a050fc1878a54d9443e71f1fee08de","tid":2176582,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7296101d4055387369d55a84fdea0c2a1222922","tid":2176582,"uid":237005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:42:49.000Z","msg":"陳X柱mode: 點解你唔問青少年對香煙同酒精有誤解？係咪因為佢地合法就無傷害？<br />\n<br />\n既然大麻有害要禁，煙同酒都應該要禁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:44:24.000Z","msg":"無錯全部禁晒佢<br />\n咪等班毒友嘈生晒"},{"pid":"3131f8febe9456b52b6c96904866fd952ec45dab","tid":2176582,"uid":10587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cacdb69db20782b87b62a6235d31b94ca41e0dcc","tid":2176582,"uid":21063,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"影響智力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/branded_news/7727/production/_103330503_musk3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7727%2Fproduction%2F_103330503_musk3.jpg&h=cf757ff4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:51:08.000Z","msg":"佢真係日日食？"},{"pid":"ea269268f7fb54cd3e348f0c2036fbe58a36ab1f","tid":2176582,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9be74822d13f72280c85f7e595c75120e8d83b88","tid":2176582,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"青協指有青少年誤解大麻傷害 籲加強教育糾正失實資訊<br />\n2020-08-27 HKT 12:56<br />\n<br />\n&quot;一項有關青少年對大麻的認知及態度的調查發現，部分青少年對大麻存在明顯誤解，近3成半受訪者認為大麻對大腦的傷害比煙酒少，逾3成表示因為部分國家將消遣用大麻合法化，所以大麻帶來的傷害不大，亦有近3成不同意大麻是毒品......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;青協深宵青年服務單位主任李智廣......指出，大麻的禍害不容忽視，長期和大量使用會損害大腦發展及降低智力，吸食大麻亦有機會造成情緒大起大落&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546178-20200827.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546178-20200827.htm&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=3d44cd07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546178-20200827.htm&h=6d2f9b16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546178-20200827.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:53:26.000Z","msg":"青協為左煙稅會去到幾盡？"},{"pid":"9f081126769ded4a404bd5d66af8b39c1407a8db","tid":2176582,"uid":15121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b890f3e1ef84247dae1a7239133a8d433fb8409","tid":2176582,"uid":203889,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"bc0337339712a30a98cbf04bfb8c6e528303757c","tid":2176582,"uid":220942,"like":29,"dislike":7,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"咁點解外國可以大麻合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T19:04:36.000Z","msg":"其實青協無講錯<br />\n如果份量唔岩，或者長期食，係會影響身體<br />\n<br />\n不過唔止大麻，其他substance都會有負面影響但合法，例如煙酒<br />\n淨係禁大麻唔禁煙，雙重標準"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:54:13.000Z","msg":"其實好多野都係<br />\n份量唔岩，或者長期食，係會影響身體"},{"pid":"0c804bd80f9bb5dcc2e99198f8f046625b5a8283","tid":2176582,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:06:06.000Z","msg":"smoke weed everyday"},{"pid":"ed11c4ca7118670960d12a83a17d6bb6dd38d7e4","tid":2176582,"uid":78519,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0c804bd80f9bb5dcc2e99198f8f046625b5a8283","tid":2176582,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:06:06.000Z","msg":"smoke weed everyday"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:07:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">誰說大麻不會成癮？年輕人吸食兩次就精神分裂</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本身是精神科專科醫生的香港青協青年違法防治中心義務顧問張偉謙指出，大麻含有的四氫大麻酚（簡稱THC）會影響大腦功能，可引致協調障礙、集中力減弱、記憶力及判斷力受損，亦會破壞呼吸系統，嚴重者會產生幻覺、幻聽、憂鬱及對別人極度懷疑，容易激動及脾氣暴躁等，而且容易上癮，「需越吸食越多才可以止癮」，並非如網上資訊所述，吸食大麻不會上癮。<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》報導，張偉謙表示，曾有一名20出頭的男性求診者只是吸食大麻兩次，就出現精神分裂，「他之前未接觸過毒品，只是食了兩次大麻就出事」。他指出，外國文獻指部份人因遺傳因素，吸食大麻有機會誘發精神分裂症，指大腦成長期是由人出生至24歲，「若在大腦成長期間食大麻，會影響大腦發育」。<br />\n<br />\n另有外國研究發現，吸食大麻會令腦部衰退，或會出現認知障礙症。張偉謙還提到，另有病人最初吸食大麻，其後吸食冰毒，兩年後出現幻聽幻覺等精神病病徵，稱以其臨床經驗，約有兩成半吸食大麻的求診者在停止吸食大麻後，仍持續出現幻聽幻覺等病徵。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"827575ffa2e4bb540f996949e9341bdddb019125","tid":2176582,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f081126769ded4a404bd5d66af8b39c1407a8db","tid":2176582,"uid":15121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b890f3e1ef84247dae1a7239133a8d433fb8409","tid":2176582,"uid":203889,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"bc0337339712a30a98cbf04bfb8c6e528303757c","tid":2176582,"uid":220942,"like":29,"dislike":7,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"咁點解外國可以大麻合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T19:04:36.000Z","msg":"其實青協無講錯<br />\n如果份量唔岩，或者長期食，係會影響身體<br />\n<br />\n不過唔止大麻，其他substance都會有負面影響但合法，例如煙酒<br />\n淨係禁大麻唔禁煙，雙重標準"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T21:54:13.000Z","msg":"其實好多野都係<br />\n份量唔岩，或者長期食，係會影響身體"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:27:26.000Z","msg":"而家討論緊drugs麻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HurjftO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHurjftO.gif&h=1256f4b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0364501f6e292547e9168cba316c8a9dfdf42a6","tid":2176582,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:35:42.000Z","msg":"連登道友又衝晒出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a9e49ec53a589e97a83607ee094daca5f9b6fb","tid":2176582,"uid":7409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"827575ffa2e4bb540f996949e9341bdddb019125","tid":2176582,"uid":203889,"like":1,"disli